<HL>    Politics & Policy:
@  Reno Is Expected to Pick
@  Whitewater Counsel Soon </HL>
<DD> 01/19/94 </DD>
<SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A20 </SO>
<IN> ALL REGIONAL BANKS (BAR), SOUTHERN U.S. BANKS (BAS), ALL BANKS (BNK),
   REAL ESTATE INVESTMENTS (REA), SAVINGS & LOANS, THRIFTS (SAL) </IN>
<DATELINE> WASHINGTON </DATELINE>
<TXT>
<p>
   Attorney General Janet Reno is expected to announce
soon the name of the special counsel who will examine matters
surrounding President Clinton's investment in Whitewater Development
Corp.
</p>
<p>
   A Justice Department official said the announcement may come as
early as today, "but that would be quite a push." Ms. Reno was
traveling between Friday and last night and planned to review names
